ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This project (NTLMSRH) is a modernized enhancement of the original NTLMRecon 
tool created by Sachin Kamath (@pwnfoo). While this is a complete rewrite with 
significant enhancements and new features, we acknowledge and respect the 
original concept and inspiration provided by NTLMRecon.

Original NTLMRecon: https://github.com/pwnfoo/NTLMRecon
Original Author: Sachin Kamath (@pwnfoo)

The original NTLMRecon was also inspired by:
- NTLMScan concept by @nyxgeek

This enhanced version includes:
- Complete Python 3 rewrite
- Multi-threading support  
- Modern error handling
- Enhanced output formatting
- JSON/CSV reporting capabilities
- CIDR range support
- Session management
- Request retry logic
- And many other improvements

We encourage users to check out the original NTLMRecon project and support
the original authors who created the foundation for this work.